  <brief_title>Effect of Subcision and Suction on Acne Scars</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Split Face Randomized, Evaluator Blinded Study on the Effect of Subcision and Suctioning With a Microdermabrasion Device on Rolling Acne Scars</official_title>
  <sponsors>
